esul Bucure\u0219ti|Progresul Bucure\u015fti]]\n\n<!--Status-->\n|status_DIN=C\n|status_UCJ=R\n|status_UTA=R\n|status_PRO=R\n\n<!--Table settings and rules-->\n|show_limit=5\n|class_rules=Rules for classification: 1) points; 2) goal difference; 3) number of goals scored\n\n<!--Qualification and relegation column definitions-->\n|res_col_header=QR\n|col_EC  = green1     |text_EC  = Qualification to [[1982\u201383 European Cup#Preliminary round|European Cup preliminary round]]\n<!--|col_CWC = yellow1    |text_CWC = Qualification to [[1982\u201383 European Cup Winners' Cup#First round|Cup Winners' Cup first round]]-->\n|col_UC  = blue1      |text_UC  = Qualification to [[1982\u201383 UEFA Cup#First round|UEFA Cup first round]]\n<!--|col_BK  = lightgreen |text_BK  = Qualification to [[1982 Balkans Cup|Balkans Cup]]-->\n|col_REL = red1       |text_REL = Relegation to [[1982\u201383 Divizia B|Divizia B]]\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Top goalscorers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"50px\" |Position\n! Player\n! Club\n! width=\"50px\" | Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=1 align=\"center\"|1\n| [[Anghel Iord\u0103nescu]]\n| [[FC Steaua Bucure\u015fti|Steaua Bucure\u015fti]]\n|align=center|20\n|-\n|rowspan=1 align=\"center\"|2\n| [[Sorin C\u00e2r\u0163u]]\n| [[FC Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]]\n|align=center|19\n|-\n|rowspan=1 align=\"center\"|3\n| [[Sorin G\u00e2ngu]]\n| [[Chimia R\u00e2mnicu V\u00e2lcea]]\n|align=center|16\n|-\n|rowspan=1 align=\"center\"|4\n| [[Gheorghe Iamandi]]\n| [[FC Olt Scornice\u015fti|Olt Scornice\u015fti]]\n|align=center|14\n|-\n|rowspan=1 align=\"center\"|5\n| [[Ioan Petcu]]\n| [[Corvinul Hunedoara]]\n|align=center|13\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n\n* [[1981\u201382 Divizia B]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Liga I seasons}}\n{{1981\u201382 in European football (UEFA)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1981-82 Divizia A}}\n[[Category:Liga I seasons]]\n[[Category:1981\u201382 in European association football leagues|Romania]]\n[[Category:1981\u201382 in Romanian 