926 |first=Champat Rai |last=Jain |authorlink=Champat Rai Jain |url=https://archive.org/details/SannyasaDharma |ref={{sfnref|Champat Rai Jain|1926}} }}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Commonscatinline}}\n*[http://www.idjo.org International Digamber Jain Organization]\n\n{{Jainism topics}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Nudity in religion]]\n[[Category:Digambara| ]]\n", "name_user": "Aayushmamu04", "label": "safe", "comment": "I have just Added a Photo of a Prominent Digambara Jain Monk Acharya Vishuddh Sagar ji maharaj.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digambara"}
